org.apache.jena.hadoop.rdf.types

Class NodeWritable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.hadoop.rdf.types.NodeWritable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<NodeWritable>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<NodeWritable>

    public class NodeWritable
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<NodeWritable>
    A writable for Node instances

    This uses RDF Thrift for the binary encoding of terms. The in-memory storage for this type is both a Node and a RDF_Term with lazy conversion between the two forms as necessary.
